- Version/Release
- Last updated date
- GitHub stars (engagement indicator)

**Development Status**:
- Active/Inactive status
- Development stage (alpha, beta, stable)
- Maintenance status

**Social/Engagement**:
- Downloads count
- Contributors count
- Activity indicators

**Badge Implementation**:

